    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🤖 Content Strategist AI\n\nTakes your topic → generates all content for LinkedIn + Twitter.\n\n🔑 Get Gemini API Key\n1. https://aistudio.google.com → Get API Key\n2. Key starts with AIza...\n3. n8n → Credentials → Google PaLM → paste key\n   Save as \"Google Gemini(PaLM) Api account\"\n\n",
