      "name": "Sticky Note1"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🎨 Generate Image — Hugging Face\n\nModel: Stable Diffusion XL\nInput: image_prompt from AI node\nOutput: PNG binary → flows to LinkedIn + Twitter\n\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🔑 Get Hugging Face Token\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n1. Go to https://huggingface.co\n2. Click \"Sign Up\" → fill name, email, password\n3. Verify your email → log in\n4. Click your profile picture (top right)\n5. Go to \"Settings\"\n6. Click \"Access Tokens\" from left menu\n7. Click \"New Token\"\n8. Fill in:\n   • Name: anything (e.g. n8n-workflow)\n   • user permission : select all \n9. Click \"Generate Token\"\n10. Copy the token → starts with hf_...\n⚠️ Copy it now — you cannot see it again later\n\n\nWhere to paste:\nNode → Headers → Authorization → Bearer hf_yourtoken\n\n",
        "height": 576,
        "width": 560
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -48,
        1536
      ],
      "id": "60b2d990-4e09-4343-a139-e6321b00a02f",
      "name": "Sticky Note2"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🪪 getid — Fetch Person ID\n\nGET https://api.linkedin.com/v2/userinfo\n\nRun once → find \"sub\" in response = your Person ID\n\nPaste it here:\n- Register Upload → \"owner\": \"urn:li:person:YOURID\"\n- Create Post → \"author\": \"urn:li:person:YOURID\"\n\n",
        "height": 560,
        "width": 736
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        672,
        176
      ],
      "id": "6b27a181-11b7-4e9b-af1c-21b475cef26c",
      "name": "Sticky Note3"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 1️⃣ LinkedIn Native Post (Primary)\n\nUses n8n built-in LinkedIn OAuth2 node.\n\nn8n Setup:\nCredentials → LinkedIn OAuth2 API\n→ paste Client ID + Client Secret → Connect\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🔑 Get Client ID & Client Secret\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n1. Go to https://linkedin.com/developers/apps\n2. Open your App → go to \"Auth\" tab\n3. You will see:\n   • Client ID → copy it\n   • Client Secret → click \"show\" → copy it\n\n",
        "height": 368,
        "width": 560
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        544,
        1216
      ],
      "id": "fa31222a-4cb5-4475-859d-4bc1f76ba4c4",
      "name": "Sticky Note4"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 2️⃣ Fallback Step 1 — Register Upload\n\nPOST https://api.linkedin.com/v2/assets?action=registerUpload\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🔐 Header Auth Setup in this node\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n1. Open this node → go to Authentication section\n2. Set \"Authentication\" → Generic Credential Type\n3. Set \"Generic Auth Type\" → Header Auth\n4. In \"Credential for Header Auth\" →\n   select \"Header Auth account\"\n   (if not created yet → click New):\n   • Name:  Authorization\n   • Value: Bearer <your LinkedIn token>\n   • Save as \"Header Auth account\"\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n⚠️ Replace Person ID in JSON body\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nFind this line in the JSON body:\n\"owner\": \"urn:li:person:g5yec9SDhg\"\nReplace g5yec9SDhg with your actual Person ID\n(get it from the getid node → \"sub\" field)\n\n",
        "height": 656,
        "width": 544
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1520,
        1296
      ],
      "id": "668888c4-3dbe-49ed-890b-fb2510e05f6c",
      "name": "Sticky Note5"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 3️⃣ Fallback Step 2 — Upload Image\n\nPUT <uploadUrl from Register step>\n\nCredential: Header Auth account\n\n⚠️ Token is hardcoded in this node:\nHeaders → Authorization → Bearer AQV...\nReplace with your token. Update every 60 days.\n\nBody: binary image (data field), Content-Type: image/png",
        "height": 416,
        "width": 480
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        2304,
        1280
      ],
      "id": "14e19812-1414-4826-8bcd-ba0901d4e42b",
      "name": "Sticky Note6"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 4️⃣ Fallback Step 3 — Create Post\n\nPOST https://api.linkedin.com/v2/ugcPosts\n\nCredential: Header Auth account\n\n⚠️ Replace both hardcoded values:\n1. Headers → Authorization → Bearer <your_token>\n2. JSON body → \"author\": \"urn:li:person:YOURID\"\n\n",
        "height": 416,
        "width": 512
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        2880,
